rows.label: tlk41300012_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Well, I hear Chairman Bahn's
been de-chaired.

rows.label: tlk41300012_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Can't say I'm surprised. We all knew
he was involved in shady business.

rows.label: tlk41300012_03_msg0003
rows.name:
He had some wacky business venture
going on in Superbia, I hear.

rows.label: tlk41300012_03_msg0004
rows.name:
And he was trying to turn it over
to Iira, or something or other.

rows.label: tlk41300012_03_msg0005
rows.name: Yeah, that's not OK in my book.

rows.label: tlk41300012_03_msg0006
rows.name:
In the meantime, Nilny's taken over
as interim chairman. Wonder how long
it'll be before a new one's appointed?

rows.label: tlk41300012_03_msg0007
rows.name:
They'll have to hurry it up a bit if they
don't want to lose out on deals...
